pageProduct.description:
General Information

Veet for Men Hair Removal Normal Cream is suitable to remove hair on your chest, legs, back, arms and underarms.

Experience Veet Men Hair Removal Cream with Silk & Fresh™ Technology. Whilst removing hair, Veet not only hydrates skin for up to 24 hours, but its fragrance technology is designed to leave no lingering malodour.

It's easy, only apply for 3*-6 minutes to enjoy smooth skin.

 *Starts working from 3 minutes

Size: 200mL

KEY FEATURES

• Quick and Easy
• Hydrates Skin For Up To 24 Hours
• Takes between 3*-6 minutes
• No Lingering Malodour
